   641→## Implementation Plan
   642→
   643→### Phase 1: Core Abstraction (15-20 min)
   644→
   645→**T1.1** Create `AIClient` interface (5 min)
   646→
   647→- File: `packages/classification-engine/src/ai/ai-client.ts`
   648→- Define `AIClient`, `ChatCompletionParams`, `ChatCompletionResponse`
   649→- Add JSDoc comments explaining abstraction purpose
   650→
   651→**T1.2** Create `OpenAIClient` implementation (5 min)
   652→
   653→- File: `packages/classification-engine/src/ai/openai-client.ts`
   654→- Implement `AIClient` interface
   655→- Wrap OpenAI SDK's `chat.completions.create()` method
   656→- Add error handling for missing API key
   657→
   658→**T1.3** Export from package index (2 min)
   659→
   660→- File: `packages/classification-engine/src/index.ts`
   661→- Export `AIClient` interface (for use in email-processor tests)
   662→- Do NOT export `OpenAIClient` (internal implementation detail)
   663→
   664→**T1.4** Run TypeScript compilation (3 min)
   665→
   666→```bash
   667→npm run build --workspace=@gmail-automation/classification-engine
   668→```
